						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1478 (1555 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Refers to an endowment of money. The details of the gift are lost. The details of the date, <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1478, Rākshasa, Chaitra, ••••• dvādaśi</hi> are insufficient for verification. They may be equated with <hi rend="bold">1555 A.D., April 3 (śu. 12) or April 18 (ba. 12).</hi> </p>						

